Package: SC19052
Type: Package
Title: Functions for collective risk model and risk measures
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-12-30
Author: Hongfang Sun
Maintainer: Hongfang Sun <sunhf@mail.ustc.edu.cn>
Description: There are three R functions which can compute the cumulative loss for collective risk model,
         and a drawing function for risk measures which can draw the curve of VaR and TVaR changing 
         with quantile level.
